===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-level.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛvəl|-ɛvəl]]

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more-most}}

# The same height at all places.
#:''This table isn't quite level &mdash; see how this marble rolls off it?''
# Being [[unvaried]]
# Being [[sensible]]
#:''He kept a level head under stress.''

